1004
01:00:22,277 --> 01:00:23,470
Pelakunya!

1005
01:00:24,478 --> 01:00:25,546
Tidak!

1006
01:00:25,547 --> 01:00:26,847
Jika kita kalah hari ini,
kontrak kita akan dibatalkan.

1007
01:00:26,848 --> 01:00:28,317
